     const inventory = [{ id: 1, quantity: 10 }];
     const orders = [{ itemId: 1, quantity: 5 }];

     processOrders(orders, inventory);
     expect(inventory[0].quantity).toBe(5);
   });
   ```

2. **Performance Benchmarking**  
   Use a benchmarking tool like [Benchmark.js](https://benchmarkjs.com/) to compare the performance of the original and optimized versions.

   Example:

   ```js
